    "billing_flow": [
      "1. Supplier purchases energy in day-ahead market based on aggregated forecasts",
      "2. Supplier adjusts position in intra-day market based on updated forecasts",
      "3. Actual consumption/generation measured at individual meters",
      "4. Supplier handles all imbalances in balancing market",
      "5. Supplier bills customers based on retail prices for net consumption",
      "6. Prosumers receive feed-in tariff for net exports to grid"
